        "id": 2722503,
        "name": "Dave Sankaran",
        "username": "Dave_Sankaran",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/9fc29f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-09-26T16:05:17.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>(I also cross-posted this in the travel forum)</p>\n<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>I\u2019m attending a wedding in Mailly-la-Ville next weekend and I\u2019m hoping to buy a nice magnum of Burgundy to give as a gift while I\u2019m there.  Thinking of heading into Beaune early on the wedding day and hoping to locate something nice to gift them.  Any suggestions on where and what?</p>\n<p>Thanks,<br>\nDave</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 8,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-03T13:35:59.238Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
