      {
        "id": 2722519,
        "name": "A Songeur",
        "username": "A_Songeur",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/46a35a/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-09-26T16:18:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Best is to visit a producer you like\u2026 possibly with a phone call before.</p>\n<p>Other plan if no time nor knowledge: It is wine fair in supermarkets\u2026 you may find some good stuff at decent prices\u2026 alternative is on the main road between Beaune, Nuits, Vosne\u2026 you have quite a few wine producers who sell wine with age.<br>\nIf you cannot be bothered, there are plenty of wine shops where you can get great advice but probably have to pay slightly higher price</p>",
        "post_number": 2,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 8,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-03T13:36:00.530Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
