        "created_at": "2019-09-26T16:56:38.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The Athenaeum book store also has an excellent wine selection. The Grand Boutique du Vin off the avenue Charles de Gaulle a ways outside of town also has a great selection.</p>",
