        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/67e7ee/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-09-26T18:05:46.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I predict in the future the prices will be higher\u2026if you find out anyone who does this, let me know. I suspect that there is little interest in futures offerings with most producers. If they have a good reputation, practically everything from name producers is fought over by importers these days like a juicy bone.</p>",
